        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/First.20steps.20in.20linear.20algebra/near/497290721\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Most continuous functions on <code>Real</code> are computable</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>Real.abs</code> is continuous but I don't think it will be computable (but I'm not an expert on this stuff), and in some sense most continuous functions look much worse than <code>Real.abs</code>.</p>",
